>	<li>材料科学工程硕士（M.Eng in Materials Science &amp; Engineering）：为期1年，共计修读25个学期学分，以就业导向为主，是专业硕士项目。要求申请者本科毕业，拥有工程学、物理、化学或相关专业背景。不接受已获得博士学位的申请者。不提供任何形式的奖学金*(5)</li></ul><p><strong>专业设置</strong></p><p>加州大学伯克利分校材料科学与工程系开设的相关研究领域有：</p><ul>	<li>生物材料（Biomaterials）</li>	<li>化学与电化学材料（Chemical and Electrochemical Materials）</li>	<li>计算材料（Computational Materials）</li>	<li>电磁与光材料（Electronic, Magnetic and Optical Materials）</li>	<li>结构材料（Structural Materials）*(6)</li></ul><p>外部链接：</p><ul>	<li>加州大学伯克利分校材料科学与工程系研究生导师列表：<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=CrXRF8zJkIT16Eg0tttttt29KWI7X392cRbzbzqy36MaPGS5RCzkDxBy4N9QgDZkSyu4vGVjqxPrha_4WzIrPw' target='_blank'>Faculty</a></li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=DroIGDOqLtcCKxMWLLLLLdVLrj5hOZL79ZXujzEjaj5Ll0rmRmAr4Wgr3GxcMQi56vFUozu6qzRCnkBgeNL8IZ2nSpz8HzEMaGM1c5kbEAcZylcDplDqKHKf46jD8g9oTCHCM_8dXpzo' target='_blank'>2019-20&nbsp;Fee Schedule</a> UC Berkeley</p><p>(2) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=UrsQlJEhwkcdGHPmzillRNFE3PNzmnFF85Xm_FdcBuHvwyFaBzDmipS9UFzjm6FnbRdd6rxkIJnQd3rxkVMpyOaqqaqfDKdZIT0xI3LFqEJc_V6iFnNH' target='_blank'>Graduate Admissions</a> UC Berkeley</p><p>(3) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=WrSJLFTuwN_n-CkU7laK1Rf30B3EVDaB0PaJg9PCdXg62ycWazCaG-fflhfTElAoiy-O5exIYRycdSY1TrpOv' target='_blank'>Graduate</a> UC Berkeley</p><p>(4) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=wrYmhljzkc7SCZaRMMMMMMOYqg1yVeKbUAlRlR4pTLB1wotS5_vWt-qxk2c25zt0XfFRAFYsSF8sKAUmMAkE' target='_blank'>Admissions FAQ</a> UC Berkeley</p><p>(5) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=1rdft_3TLNk2BiqVt5Pstv-B_zac_kRq3cWe5JJ1SfEqoej17SZVLIMMwMwWq2Z_q30tio9L-GjLS_dpiMppqwFDCkEPGHS_JAn8pfN' target='_blank'>Master of Engineering Degree</a> UC Berkeley</p><p>(6) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=pr9ExTH3kCscvfGAWWWWWWZ6iTKAMkyehni5i5XeAQQK-0VxIbl4EyGh76TseyACITsY7dWmUdYkI' targ