 Signaling</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:53.88%">			<p>生物修复</p>			</td>			<td style="width:46.12%">			<p>Bioremediation</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:53.88%">			<p>生物矿化</p>			</td>			<td style="width:46.12%">			<p>Biomineralization</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:53.88%">			<p>病毒学</p>			</td>			<td style="width:46.12%">			<p>Virology</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:53.88%">			<p>大数据</p>			</td>			<td style="width:46.12%">			<p>Big Data</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:53.88%">			<p>光合作用</p>			</td>			<td style="width:46.12%">			<p>Photosynthesis</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:53.88%">			<p>生物燃料</p>			</td>			<td style="width:46.12%">			<p>Biofuels</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:53.88%">			<p>细胞结构</p>			</td>			<td style="width:46.12%">			<p>Cell Structure</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:53.88%">			<p>菌类</p>			</td>			<td style="width:46.12%">			<p>Fungi</p>			</td>		</tr>	</tbody></table><p>*(4)</p><p>外部链接：</p><ul>	<li>教员列表：<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=ArAjQunawJr7tgDz777777ICMmHIk0LUNItW3VOjOV_dCp_9-4N61jDJcr-nl_RqmnBbWca' target='_blank'>Faculty</a></li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=DroIGDyEkoeaLlo3I9c1iSPTRDviuccPZx97ftqn_d0ULVJjY3TllpUCx63VWlw7IMLCXwCj0xp2RpsGM6dgVRwscr60tY_doGLVWpNPZSQ8RUIo_DIh' target='_blank'>2019-2020&nbsp;Tuition and Fees</a>&nbsp;UC Berkeley</p><p>(2) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=ArAjQuFDkbcX2tfCAAAAAApA5Ls6kVrtd3FHZoLgLJJ9fGJp8uKoX4AtBDM37fek7x4k8yY2igsvBjjqxur51' target='_blank'>Graduate Programs</a> PMB Department, UC Berkeley</p><p>(3)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=_r75g1xLks07EeJL------ocqNFolfovL3NgkK9E9PHBOtTZ0PEoGPTKd8Ty6Ixs' target='_blank'>Financial Assistance</a>&nbsp;UC Berkeley</p><p>(4) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=MrO2caRlL7YsCTBVEEEEEE61DAUI