(e.g., honors thesis).</li>	<li>Very strong letters of recommendations from at least two faculty members who know the candidate in both classroom and out-of-class settings (e.g. independent research).</li>	<li>Statement of purpose that expresses coherent ideas about why the candidate is interested in pursuing a Ph.D. in economics and describes likely areas of research interest.</li>	<li>TOEFL (if applicable) at least 570 for the paper-and-pencil test, at least 230 for the computer-based test, or at least 68 for the Internet-based test (iBT).</li></ul><p>简译：</p><ul>	<li>GPA3.8以上，同时还会考虑其课业的实际难度</li>	<li>高等<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%A6' target='_blank'>数学</a>，包括实变函数、微积分等成绩A-以上，也即85分以上</li>	<li>GRE数学163分以上</li>	<li><a href='http://www.qianmu.org/%E5%BE%AE%E8%A7%82%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E5%AD%A6' target='_blank'>微观经济学</a>、<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/%E5%AE%8F%E8%A7%82%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E5%AD%A6' target='_blank'>宏观经济学</a>及<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/%E8%AE%A1%E9%87%8F%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E5%AD%A6' target='_blank'>计量经济学</a>成绩A-以上，数学方向表现良好</li>	<li>学习过高等经济学课程</li>	<li>具备独立研究能力</li>	<li>强<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/%E6%8E%A8%E8%8D%90%E4%BF%A1' target='_blank'>推荐信</a>（至少包括两名同时熟悉学生的课堂内及课堂外（如独立研究）表现的教师的推荐信）</li>	<li>表述清晰兴趣明确的<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E9%99%88%E8%BF%B0' target='_blank'>个人陈述</a></li>	<li>TOEFL网考不低于90分*(5)</li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=PrgaXqIdkfKZOJg0ttttttgxYcP8B4mFrnZQsZUKYnv83d3Qy66u_13rjcZyLFksNsoGpJtPafocaJ81vR_FLFtPQJeGwRoBad8V' target='_blank'>2019-2020&nbsp;Tuition and Fees</a>&nbsp;UC Berkeley</p><p>(2)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=MrO2caJQwtelkDCTaaaaaaP1O7K3g7zyOWqScpcJ8sSJ3kgVbV2PGAbPXFOKaWnUKFwGeOjiJOsmJi6xQlZHIlVvxfDqx_EX5V' target='_blank'>Frequently Asked Questions</a> Department of Economics,&nbsp;UC Berkeley</p><p>(3)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=-rGz4OcBLpMoTc_lr9mf